                                                    Back-to-school spending expected to reach $27 billion: Deloitte
                                                


                                                    MarketWatch – 
                                                    9:22 AM ET 07/12/2017
                                                


Back-to-school spending is expected to reach $27 billion in sales, according to the latest survey from Deloitte. More than a quarter of shoppers will shop at off-price retailers, like T.J. Maxx, a TJX Cos (TJX). chain, a 10 percentage-point rise from last year.

















